No connection that I can see.

I don't think those are connected in any way.

No, I don't see any connection at all.

I really hope we're not wasting our time here.

Why? Have you got something more important to do?

Yes. Not freezing to death.

I suppose if a building had to be haunted, it would be one like this.

No accounting for taste, I guess.

I don't think Durkin's coming.

Thought as much. I told you before, you can't put much faith in cops.

If I didn't need the money, I'd be tempted to just blow Durkin off and go home.

Well, we're here anyway. We might as well check the place out before calling it a wash.

We're beyond that now. There's a spook here, and that makes it our problem. Not his.

