Plausible deniability, Red. What did you expect?

I don't know. A bit of courtesy?

Think about it. He can't let on that he's hired someone like you, can he?

So he's gotta keep his distance. That way, if anybody asks, he doesn't have to lie.

Great. So I'm the NYPD's dirty little secret.

I knew you'd do me proud one day.

Any of these names ring any bells?

You kidding? I can barely read anything on that tiny screen.

So what's she like? The ghost, I mean.

Incoherent. Babbling. A total basket case. Typical spook, in other words.

