Uh huh. So?

We find the phone, we find...

I don't know. A clue. Or something.

Do you have any better ideas? No? Okay.

I know that there are a lot of self-help groups in New York, but I've never heard of any that could do... that.

Whoever they are, we'll get to the bottom of it. I promise you that.

Whoever this Michael is, he seems to know a lot about who we are.

Then that makes him number one on our most wanted list.

