No, but I don't exactly follow the arts these days.

It sounds like "The River Wall" was a dud.

Not necessarily. One review is still just one person's opinion.

The cops sure cleared this place out in a hurry.

Course, they left a mess behind. Which we have to clean up.

Jesus. The look on that guy's face...

